title: Children's Picture Dictionary with General Knowledge (gnv64)
description:
Children's Picture Dictionary with General Knowledge
Arora Book Co.| English/Hindi | PDF | 192 pages | 25.8 mb
scanned to PDF by me.

This is a bilingual pictorial dictionary for kids. Common English words are defined in both languages with the help of coloured pictures. Second half is on GK with English words for colours, days, months, animals, body parts, insects, birds, time, souds, places, subjects, flowers, fruits, vegetables, sports & games, plants, trees, relations etc translated into Hindi.
